title: Bringing Back Queenie Theory Video
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I really hope her character ends up striking a deal with Papa Legba, he seemed to like her and regardless of how she is brought back - I want to see Papa Legba again! Such a cool character with an interesting tie to Queenie!
Its so crazy to think that this show has been on for 7 years already!! Feels like it went by in a flash

I love Queenie.. a damn human voodoo doll and a witch. 

Imma need more backstory 👏🏾 like who is Queenie's biological mother?

To add to the idea that she survived in Hotel, Queenie wasn't in the last episode of Hotel when Liz and Iris had all of the ghosts meet together. This may or may not have been intentional on the writers' part, but it adds to the fact that she was never shown in Hotel as a ghost.
Butbutbut what I wanna know is--- Did she win on "The Price is Right"?
